						<summary>

						<p>This is damaged and seems to register an endowment of 28 <hi rend="italic">kaḻañju</hi> and odd of gold by one Tāḻi Kumaraṉ of Teṅgūr in Nalaṅgiḷinallūr-kūṟṟam to provide for feeding two Brāhmaṇas in the temple daily with the interest thereon, and another gift of money for burning two perpetual lamps, before the deity.</p>						

